# RAG Based Question Answering System

A simple Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system built with:

- Python
- Ollama
- BGE-M3 Embeddings
- Qwen3 LLM
- Scikit-learn Cosine Similarity

This project retrieves the most relevant text chunks using vector similarity and generates answers using a local LLM.

---

# Features

- Local embedding generation using `bge-m3`
- Semantic search with cosine similarity
- Retrieval of top relevant chunks
- Answer generation using `qwen3:8b`
- Fast vector search using NumPy + scikit-learn
- Offline/local AI workflow with Ollama

